org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler

Class HBaseVertexHandler<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseElementHandler
      • org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseGraphElementHandler
        • org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseVertexHandler<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - EPGM vertex type
    E - EPGM edge type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ElementHandler, GraphElementHandler, VertexHandler<V,E>

    public class HBaseVertexHandler<V extends EPGMVertex,E extends EPGMEdge>
extends HBaseGraphElementHandler
implements VertexHandler<V,E>
    Used to read/write EPGM vertex data from/to a HBase table.

    EPGMVertex data in HBase:

    |---------|--------------------|---------|-------------|-------------| | row-key | meta | data | out-edges | in-edges | |---------|----------|---------|---------|-------------|-------------| | "0" | label | graphs | k1 | k2 | <0.1.knows> | <1.0.knows> | | |----------|---------|----|----|-------------|-------------| | | "Person" | [0,2] | v1 | v2 | | | |---------|----------|---------|----|----|-------------|-------------|

    See Also:
